emic), elephants and leopards.","image":{"src":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1f/Chinnar_Wildlife_Sanctuary%2C_Munnar_-_panoramio.jpg","alt":"Chinnar Wildlife Sanctuary"},"photos":["https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1f/Chinnar_Wildlife_Sanctuary%2C_Munnar_-_panoramio.jpg","https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6f/Chinnar_Wildlife_Sanctuary%2C_Munnar_-_panoramio_%281%29.jpg","https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fa/Chinnar_Wildlife_Sanctuary%2C_Munnar_-_panoramio_%282%29.jpg"]},{"name":"Lockhart Gap","category":"scenic","distance":"14 km","entryFee":"Free","timings":"All day","duration":"1 hr","rating":4.3,"description":"Mountain pass with sweeping views over Rajamala and Anamudi peaks. Less crowded.","image":{"src":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7c/The_1984_painting_%22Matilda_Lockhart_Comes_Home%2C%22_by_artist_Lee_Herring%2C_displayed_at_the_Buffalo_Gap_Historic_Village_in_the_unincorporated_Taylor_County%2C_Texas%2C_town_of_the_same_name%2C_near_Abilene_LCCN2014631318.tif/lossy-page1-1280px-thumbnail.tif.jpg","alt":"Lockhart Gap"},"photos":["https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7c/The_1984_painting_%22Matilda_Lockhart_Comes_Home%2C%22_by_artist_Lee_Herring%2C_displayed_at_the_Buffalo_Gap_Historic_Village_in_the_unincorporated_Taylor_County%2C_Texas%2C_town_of_the_same_name%2C_near_Abilene_LCCN2014631318.tif/lossy-page1-1280px-thumbnail.tif.jpg","https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/65/NOMINATIONS_OF_SHELIA_BAIR%2C_JAMES_B._LOCKHART%2C_III%2C_DONALD_L._KOHN%2C_AND_KATHLEEN_L._CASEY_%28IA_gov.gpo.fdsys.CHRG-109shrg28558%29.pdf/page1-960px-NOMINATIONS_OF_SHELIA_BAIR%2C_JAMES_B._LOCKHART%2C_III%2C_DONALD_L._KOHN%2C_AND_KATHLEEN_L._CASEY_%28IA_gov.gpo.fdsys.CHRG-109shrg28558%29.pdf.jpg","https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e0/The_alleged_increase_of_lunacy_%28electronic_resource%29_-_a_farther_note_%28IA_b21479768%29.pdf/page1-500px-